Class ICalDataType

  • java.lang.Object
    • biweekly.ICalDataType

  • public class ICalDataType
extends Object
    Defines the data type of a property's value.
    Author:
    Michael Angstadt
    See Also:
    RFC 5545 p.29-50

      A URI value.
